<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Aryan ‚ù§Ô∏è Jyothi</title>

  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      height: 100vh;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9a9e, #fad0c4);
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      overflow: hidden;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .container {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 40px;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: auto;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 3em;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .heart {
      font-size: 3em;
      animation: pulse 1.5s infinite;
    }

    @keyframes pulse {
      0% { transform: scale(1); }
      50% { transform: scale(1.2); }
      100% { transform: scale(1); }
    }

    .message {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      padding: 25px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 1.1em;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    button {
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 30px;
      background: #ff3366;
      color: white;
      font-size: 1.2em;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    button:hover {
      background: #ff1744;
    }

    .popup {
      display: none;
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .popup-content {
      background: #fff;
      color: #000;
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      max-width: 400px;
    }

    .night {
      background: radial-gradient(circle, #2c003e, #000);
    }

    .candle {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 20px;
      width: 10px;
      height: 40px;
      background: orange;
      border-radius: 5px;
      animation: flicker 1s infinite;
    }

    @keyframes flicker {
      0% { opacity: 0.8; }
      50% { opacity: 1; }
      100% { opacity: 0.7; }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <audio autoplay loop>
    <source src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/audio/2022/10/16/audio_4b8a3c1b60.mp3" type="audio/mpeg">
  </audio>

  <div class="container">
    <h1>Aryan & Jyothi</h1>
    <div class="heart">‚ù§Ô∏è</div>

    <h2>Countdown to Valentine‚Äôs Day</h2>
    <h3 id="countdown"></h3>

    <div class="message">
      Hey Ammu ‚ù§Ô∏è<br><br>

      The last 6 months with you has given me romantic movie vibes ‚Äî
      going on dates, bike rides in the rain, cuddling and snuggling together,
      experiencing life all together.<br><br>

      This kind of love has been a dream for me my entire life.
      Thank you for making it a reality ü•π<br><br>

      You would make me the happiest man on Earth
      if you would be my <b>VALENTINE</b> üíç<br><br>

      XOXO üíã<br>
      Yours forever,<br>
      <b>Chinnu</b>
    </div>

    <button onclick="showPopup()">üíç Will You Be My Valentine?</button>
    <br>
    <button onclick="nightMode()">üïØÔ∏è Night Mode</button>
  </div>

  <div class="popup" id="popup">
    <div class="popup-content">
      <h2>She said YES üíñ</h2>
      <p>Our love story just got more beautiful ‚ú®</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="candle" style="left:20%"></div>
  <div class="candle" style="left:50%"></div>
  <div class="candle" style="left:80%"></div>

  <script>
    function showPopup() {
      document.getElementById("popup").style.display = "flex";
    }

    function nightMode() {
      document.body.classList.toggle("night");
    }

    // Countdown
    const target = new Date("February 14, 2026 00:00:00").getTime();
    setInterval(() => {
      const now = new Date().getTime();
      const diff = target - now;
      const days = Math.floor(diff / (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24));
      document.getElementById("countdown").innerHTML = days + " days left üíï";
    }, 1000);
  </script>
</body>
</html>
